*Ubije* ga je potpuno neočekivano. (He was killed unexpectedly.)
*Ubili* su ga u zatvoru. (They killed him in prison.)
*Ubijen* je od strane policije. (He was killed by the police.)
*Ubijanje* je bilo brzo i jednostavno. (The killing was quick and simple.)
*Ubica* je puštena na slobodu. (The killer was released.)